---
import TerminalHeader from '@/components/TerminalHeader.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TerminalMenu from '@/components/TerminalMenu.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div
    class='bg-slate-700 dark:bg-black text-white dark:text-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto font-mono mt-10 shadow-lg'
  >
    <h1 class='hidden'>Pedro Sorrentino - JavaScript Developer</h1>

    <TerminalHeader title=`Hello World! I'm Pedro` />

    <div class='my-4 space-y-2'>
      <p class='text-green-400 dark:text-rose-400'>$ cat about_me.txt</p>

      <p class='text-blue-400 dark:text-purple-300'>~/about/name:</p>
      <p class='text-slate-300 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4'>Pedro Sorrentino</p>

      <h2 class='hidden'>Role</h2>
      <p class='text-blue-400 dark:text-purple-300'>~/about/role:</p>
      <p class='text-slate-300 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4'>
        Frontend Developer | JavaScript Specialist | Modern Web Craftsman
      </p>

      <h2 class='hidden'>Specialization</h2>
      <p class='text-blue-400 dark:text-purple-300'>~/about/specialization:</p>
      <p class='text-slate-300 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4'>
        Passionate self-taught developer who turned curiosity into expertise. I
        breathe JavaScript and modern web technologies, creating efficient web
        applications that users love to interact with.
      </p>

      <h2 class='hidden'>Focus</h2>
      <p class='text-blue-400 dark:text-purple-300'>~/about/focus:</p>
      <p class='text-slate-300 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4'>
        Building blazing-fast web experiences with Next.js, Astro, and
        TypeScript. I'm obsessed with clean code, performance optimization, and
        creating interfaces that users can't resist.
      </p>

      <h2 class='hidden'>Achievements</h2>
      <p class='text-blue-400 dark:text-purple-300'>~/about/achievements:</p>
      <p class='text-slate-300 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4'>
        <span class='text-green-400 dark:text-rose-400'>✔</span> Launched and successfully
        sold multiple web projects from scratch
      </p>
      <p class='text-slate-300 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4'>
        <span class='text-green-400 dark:text-rose-400'>✔</span> Delivered high-impact
        solutions for clients across the globe
      </p>
      <p class='text-slate-300 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4'>
        <span class='text-green-400 dark:text-rose-400'>✔</span> Active open-source
        contributor, creating tools that help other developers
      </p>
      <p class='text-slate-300 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4'>
        <span class='text-green-400 dark:text-rose-400'>✔</span> Expert in JavaScript
        and modern development workflows
      </p>

      <h2 class='hidden'>About me</h2>
      <p class='text-blue-400 dark:text-purple-300'>~/about/me:</p>
      <p class='text-slate-300 dark:text-gray-300 ml-4'>
        Hey there! My coding journey started with curiosity and a browser
        console. Self-taught? Yes. Limited? Never. I've turned my passion for
        JavaScript into a craft, mastering Next.js and Astro along the way,
        while exploring Python and Rust for specific challenges. What sets me
        apart? I don't just write code – I build and ship products. From
        creating and selling my own projects to delivering solutions for clients
        worldwide, I've learned what makes applications not just work, but
        succeed. When I'm not coding, you'll find me [around the world/reading
        tech blogs/solving puzzles/contributing to open source] - I believe the
        best developers never stop learning and growing. Ready to bring my
        experience and endless enthusiasm to your next big project.
      </p>

      <TerminalMenu />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
